title: Oxford Complete ATPL Study Pack CBT (23 CD-ROMs)
description:
Oxford Complete ATPL Study Pack CBT (23 CD-ROMs)
	

This ATPL study pack includes now all ATPL CBT titles (22 CDs), and the ATPL Exam Preparation CD-ROM (1 CD).

Titles included:

    Air Law CBT
    Airframes & Systems CBT
    AC Electrics CBT
    DC Electrics CBT
    Piston Engines CBT
    Gas Turbines CBT
    Warning & Recording CBT
    Auto-Flight CBT
    Flight Instruments CBT: included 15th November 2011
    Aircraft Performance CBT
    Mass & Balance CBT
    Flight Planning CBT
    Human Performance & Limitations CBT part 1: Physiology & Health
    Human Performance & Limitations CBT part 2: Psychology
    Meteorology CBT
    General Navigation CBT
    Radio Navigation CBT: included 15th November 2011
    Operational Procedures CBT
    Principles of Flight CBT
    VFR RT Comms CBT
    VFR RT UK airspace Supplement CBT
    IFR RT Comms CBT
    ATPL Exam Preparation CD-ROM
================================================================================


* For running these CBTs make sure you are using a virtual CD/DVD drive which supports SPTD (i.e. Daemon Tools Light)
